  "title": "A white and red dot-like UFO spotted hovering over Curitiba [1997]*",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/22/a-white-and-red-dot-like-ufo-spotted-hovering-over-curitiba-1997/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-BD",
  "content": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Interrelated case with <span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;\"><a style=\"color:#000000;\" href=\"https://brazilianufoarchives.wordpress.com/2020/06/22/several-bright-white-dot-like-ufos-spotted-in-curitiba-1997/\">ARX.0.0.505</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 26th, 1997</strong>. Time: 05h30 pm. Duration: 03m40s. In Bairro Batel in Curitiba, Paraná State, a person with binoculars observed an unidentified flying object, shaped like a white and red dot, for more than three minutes. According to the witness, the sky was clear and the visibility was good when he noticed that a small and clear UFO was stationary above the Northwest region of Curitiba for as long as it was observed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.506. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Batel, Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
